Canaan RadcliffeHeadlineTom Green and the Carpet Frogs Perform in AfghanistanImage titleCanadian native Tom Green performs a live comedy show for military personnel at Kandahar Airfield, Afghanistan, March 5, 2011. The comedy show is part of the Canadian Army's effort to increase morale and welfare for troops in Kandahar.
